card_text: If you control a "Ki-sikil" monster and control a "Lil-la" monster: Activate 1 of these effects;$N●Target 1 "Ki-sikil" monster or 1 "Lil-la" monster you control and 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; switch control of those monsters.$N●Target 1 Set Spell/Trap your opponent controls; shuffle it into the Deck.$NYou can only activate 1 "Evil★Twin Present" per turn.
